sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Production
    participant A as AI Core
    participant H as Auto-Heal
    participant U as User
    
    P->>A: 🚨 High CPU Alert
    A->>A: 🔍 Root Cause Analysis
    alt Auto-Fix
        A->>H: 🛠️ Execute Scaling
        H->>P: ✅ Normalization
    else Human Needed
        A->>U: 📄 Diagnostic Report
        U->>A: ✔️ Confirm Action
    end